---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'
import ChevronsRight from '~/icons/chevrons-right.svg'
---

<Layout title="404 Not Found" noindex wide>
  <section
    class="flex min-h-[68vh] flex-col justify-center py-14 sm:py-20"
    aria-labelledby="not-found-title"
  >
    <p class="mb-6 font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-accent">Error 404</p>
    <div
      class="grid gap-8 border-y border-foreground/10 py-10 sm:py-14 md:grid-cols-[15rem_minmax(0,1fr)] md:items-center md:gap-16"
    >
      <p
        class="font-mono text-8xl font-bold leading-none text-foreground/12 sm:text-9xl"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        404
      </p>
      <div>
        <h1
          id="not-found-title"
          class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-heading1 sm:text-5xl"
        >
          找不到這個頁面
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg/8 text-foreground/68">
          網址可能已經變更，或這篇內容尚未公開。你可以回到首頁，或從文章彙整重新開始。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/" class="button">回到首頁</a>
          <a href="/posts/" class="button group">
            瀏覽文章 <ChevronsRight
              class="ml-2 size-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
